node.text: The brave officers who risked their lives to save others sacrificed so much to defend our nation. In securing our Capitol, they secured our democracy. They are heroes.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Kamala Harris on August 05, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and standing.

node.text:
The U.S. economy is projected to experience the highest economic growth rate in nearly 40 years. ⁣⁣
⁣⁣
We’re building America back better than before.⁣

node.accessibility_caption: Vice President Kamala Harris stands arm-in-arm with elected officials, including the late Congressman John Lewis, against a bright blue sky.

node.text:
The right to vote is the right that unlocks all other rights. When we cast a ballot, we decide our leaders. When we cast a ballot, we determine our future.⁣
⁣
Congress must pass the For the People Act and the John Lewis Voting Rights Advancement Act to protect our sacred right.

node.accessibility_caption: Vice President Kamala Harris hugs two young Black girls, all 3 are smiling. One of the little girls is holding a baby doll.

node.text:
The expanded Child Tax Credit is the largest middle-class tax cut in generations, and it will cut child poverty in half in America.⁣
⁣
Congress should extend these tax cuts for years to come.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Kamala Harris on July 30, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and sitting.

node.text:
Today, poll taxes have been traded for long voting lines. Property ownership restrictions for purges of voter rolls. Literacy tests for bans on drive-thru voting. ⁣
⁣
Mail-in voting limitations. Gerrymandering. It's all voter suppression by any other name—we must pass legislation to protect voting rights.
